First, you need to have Rust installed on your system. You can download it from the official website [rust-lang.org](https://www.rust-lang.org/tools/install). After installation, you can create a new Rust project by running:

```sh
cargo new serializable_rust_app
cd serializable_rust_app
```

### Adding Serde to Your Cargo.toml

Open the `Cargo.toml` file in your project directory and add `serde` and `serde_json` (if you want JSON serialization support) to your `[dependencies]` section:

```toml
[dependencies]
serde = "1.0"
serde_json = "1.0"
```

